longBusinessSummary: JTNB Bancorp, Inc. operates as the holding company for Jim Thorpe Neighborhood Bank that provides personal and business banking products and services. It offers checking and savings accounts, individual retirement accounts, and certificates of deposit; mortgage, home equity, commercial, and consumer loans; debit and credit cards; merchant processing services; and online banking services. The company was founded in 1852 and is based in Jim Thorpe, Pennsylvania.
